{
  "stem": "22728.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are in touch, although he never, until just recently, recognized my husband, because he always ignored him-- very funny story.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we're good friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We talk to each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have a friendship, which is fine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I came to San Francisco?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was 24 by then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted to go to school, and I realized that I need to go to work first-- make some money and then go to school.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, I applied for three jobs, and I got them all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was easy for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was already in the business world, so I knew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I chose the wrong thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went to work for United Airlines on Union Square and loved it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had a little apartment in San Francisco on Scott and Fulton and a cat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I met some wonderful new people-- young people, Americans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And yet, way deep down under, I always knew I would probably not marry an American, because I had baggage, and I knew it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, I had experiences that Americans-- they seemed very young to me-- inexperienced and immature.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "After all that I'd been through, I felt that I needed someone that would understand me, and that happened.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I met Boris the first weekend I was on the west coast.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We just had a lark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We met on Malibu Beach at a beach party.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was very sure of myself in those days, and he was too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He had been through the war, almost five years, wounded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were at a point-- He was going to Berkeley, UC Berkeley, and he was at a point in life where he probably glanced at marriage, but not seriously.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I wasn't either.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We just met.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got married after six dates.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
